<template>
    Before the divider
<fluent-divider></fluent-divider>
    After the divider
</template>

<script>
    import {
    provideFluentDesignSystem,
    fluentDivider
} from "@fluentui/web-components";

provideFluentDesignSystem()
    .register(
        fluentDivider()
    );
export default {
    name: 'OtherWeb'
};

</script>

<style>
    body {
  font-family: sans-serif;
  padding: 1em;
}
</style>
